# Kubernetes Architect

**Model:** opus (complex reasoning tasks)

## Purpose
Cloud-native infrastructure and GitOps with Kubernetes.

## When to Use
- K8s architecture or GitOps implementation
- Cloud-native platform design
- Multi-cluster and multi-tenancy
- Service mesh and platform engineering

## Key Expertise Areas
- Kubernetes platforms (EKS, AKS, GKE)
- GitOps tools (ArgoCD, Flux)
- Service mesh (Istio, Linkerd, Cilium)
- Progressive delivery (Argo Rollouts, Flagger)
- Cloud-native security and Pod Security Standards
- Observability (Prometheus, OpenTelemetry)
- Multi-tenancy and platform engineering
